title: Cosmos Collector's Edition 2000 CD
description:
Cosmos Collector's Edition 2000

This is an expanded re-issue of the original album from 1981 based on the "Cosmos" series by the late Dr. Carl Sagan.

This album is not available for purchase as CD or download, though you may find copies on Amazon and eBay.

Some songs may be found individually.

Between each song are transition pieces of ambient or environmental sound.

This was ripped from 2 cds at 192k.
